OL,7,FA monk at a prestigious Catholic
OL,8,Fboarding school allegedly sexually
OL,9,Fabused a teenage boy over three years,
OL,10,Fafter asking him to meet him alone
OL,11,Fafter Mass, prosecutors have told a
OL,12,Fjury.
OL,14,FMichael James Callaghan, known as
OL,15,FFather James, is on trial accused of
OL,16,Fsexually abusing two pupils while he
OL,17,Fwas a teacher and housemaster at
OL,18,FAmpleforth College, in North Yorkshire.
