OL,7,FCallaghan, 71, is alleged to have
OL,8,Frepeatedly indecently assaulted one
OL,9,Fboy over three years in the 1990s
OL,10,Fafter making him feel "special,"
OL,11,Fbuying him gifts and taking him on
OL,12,Ftrips in his car.
OL,14,FOpening the case to jurors at Teesside
OL,15,FCrown Court on Monday (12 May),
OL,16,Fprosecutor Mark McKone KC said the
OL,17,Fcomplainant told police the "sexual
OL,18,Fbit" had started when he was under 16,
OL,19,Fwith Callaghan kissing him.
