OL,7,FJurors heard Callaghan got the boy a
OL,8,Fkey cut for a room at the school that
OL,9,Fwas used for homeless people.
OL,11,FThe complainant said in his police
OL,12,Finterview that Callaghan would "take
OL,13,Fon the role of a boy I had a crush on"
OL,14,Fand they would kiss and simulate sex.
OL,16,FHe told officers he had been "guilt
OL,17,Ftripped" into going to see Callaghan
OL,18,Fand remembered "feelings of 'I don't
OL,19,Freally want to be held like this'".
