OL,7,FThe complainant said he had "been in
OL,8,Fsurvival mode" for more than 20 years,
OL,9,Fbut "with adult eyes" had said "Oh my
OL,10,FGod, that wasn't right," jurors heard.
OL,12,FAsked by police if he had ever said he
OL,13,Fdid not want these things to happen,
OL,14,Fthe complainant said: "I was in a
OL,15,Freally bad place, I was going through
OL,16,Fhell at school...I hated the sexual
OL,17,Fbit of it, where possible, I would
OL,18,Fjust avoid it"
