OL,7,FThese include making the complainant
OL,8,Fperform mouth-to-mouth resuscitation
OL,9,Fduring roleplay, where Callaghan
OL,10,Fpretended to have a heart attack on at
OL,11,Fleast four occasions.
OL,13,FThe defendant is also accused of
OL,14,Fsexually assaulting a 17-year-old boy
OL,15,Fin 2013 by grabbing his bottom after
OL,16,Fgoing to give him a hug.
OL,18,FMr McKone said the second complainant
OL,19,Fdescribed Callaghan as "a cool monk
OL,20,Fwho was popular," and told police he
OL,21,Fhad invited him for a glass of wine.
