OL,7,FMr McKone said the alleged sexual
OL,8,Fassault was "serious enough for him to
OL,9,Fcomplain about it to the police and
OL,10,Ffor him to still be affected by it
OL,11,Fmany years later".
OL,13,FCallaghan, of Moortown, Leeds, denies
OL,14,Fthe charges and the trial continues.
